{"tid":2500418,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★3月失業綜援個案達1.98萬宗　較去年1月劇增57.4%","createTime":"2021-04-22T15:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T15:10:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a13ec066757d1efb8e933547a322cae757283bf1","tid":2500418,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"因失業領取綜援的個案較2020年1月、即新冠疫情爆發初期劇增57.4%！社會福利署今（22日）公布最新領取綜合社會保障援助（綜援）的個案數字，今年3月領取綜援的個案逾22.37萬宗，較2月下跌763宗，按月跌幅為0.3%，受助總人數約31.9萬。<br />\n<br />\n社署指，今年3月因失業而領取綜援的個案有1.98萬宗，按月上升0.4%，數字較去年1月的1.25萬宗<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>劇增57.4%</strong></span>。而今年1月至3月，每月平均有856宗因失業而申請綜援的個案，較去年12月至今年2月的數字下跌3.3%；亦較去年1月至3月減少15.1%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210422/bkn-20210422180338241-0422_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210422%2Fbkn-20210422180338241-0422_00822_001.html&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrdiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=4443ed8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210422/bkn-20210422180338241-0422_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5f06524b1ee5711cf4a5c75c3ea2376d5cedf552","tid":2500418,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69101609c6e92456a35041ef6b8b8662f4445a9a","tid":2500418,"uid":372525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:10:21.000Z","msg":"樓升！ donki 多人！<br />\n<br />\n而老貓將被我 Dr_MK 旗下大將討伐！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}